    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use <a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/String.html#trim%28%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>String#trim()</code></a> method or <code>String allRemoved = myString.replaceAll(\"^\\\\s+|\\\\s+$\", \"\")</code> for trim both the end.</p>\n\n<p>For left trim:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String leftRemoved = myString.replaceAll(\"^\\\\s+\", \"\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>For right trim:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String rightRemoved = myString.replaceAll(\"\\\\s+$\", \"\");\n</code></pre>\n"
