    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To trim specific char, you can use:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String s = s.replaceAll(\"^(,|\\\\s)*|(,|\\\\s)*$\", \"\")\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Here will strip leading and trailing <strong>space</strong> and <strong>comma</strong>.</p>\n"
