  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6652687/strip-leading-and-trailing-spaces-from-java-string",
  "title" : "Strip Leading and Trailing Spaces From Java String",
  "body" : "<p>Is there a convenience method to strip any leading or trailing spaces from a Java String?</p>\n\n<p>Something like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String myString = \"  keep this  \";\nString stripppedString = myString.strip();\nSystem.out.println(\"no spaces:\" + strippedString);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Result:</p>\n\n<pre><code>no spaces:keep this\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><code>myString.replace(\" \",\"\")</code> would replace the space between keep and this.</p>\n"
}